cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the problem of intersection classification using monocular on-board passive vision, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed approach involves the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the performance of previous methods, which involves the evaluation of classification accuracy, a topic related to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
